Titolo: RimWorld

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: RimWorld is an indie top-down construction and management simulation video game by Ottawa-based developer Ludeon Studios. Originally called Eclipse Colony, it was initially released as a Kickstarter crowdfunding project in early access for Microsoft Windows, macOS, and Linux in November 2013, and was officially released on October 17, 2018. The game has received generally positive reviews from critics.